title: World Food Championships S01E01 Burger WEB-DL x264-RKSTR mp4
description:
World Food Championships on FYITM follows talented home cooks and professional chefs from across America as they compete to create dishes mouth-wateringly creative enough to win in their food category at the World Food Championships in Las Vegas. From BBQ to bacon to family recipes, there is a winner for each competition, culminating in a grand finale with a shot at winning a $50,000 prize. Co-hosted by chef, author and LA-based restaurant owner Jeffrey Saad and Dallas-based chef and Top Chef alum Tiffany Derry.

In the first round, the chefs must create a signature burger. In round two they have to add a delicious new twist to a classic patty preparation. The field is then narrowed to the top ten, and their challenge in round three is to use a mystery ingredient in their burger.
